content.description: This job is responsible for reading data from the Metal staging layer and loading it into the Bronze SCD Type 2 tables. It ensures historical tracking of changes by identifying new, changed, and unchanged records, applying the appropriate logic to insert new versions or retire old ones with end dates as part of the SCD2 process.
content.name: cdi_map_adm_contact_guidewire_bronze_load

object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS 
(
    SELECT 
        bls.batch_id,
        bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
        bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
    FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary bls
    WHERE bls.source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
    AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
    AND bls.batch_id = 
	(
        SELECT MAX(batch_id)
        FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary
        WHERE source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
        AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
    )
)
SELECT DISTINCT 
	metal_acd.source_name as src_source_name, 
	metal_acd.load_type as src_load_type, 
	metal_acd.id as src_id,
	metal_acd.agency_nup as src_agency_nup, 
	metal_acd.contact_firstname as src_contact_firstname, 
	metal_acd.contact_lastname as src_contact_lastname, 
	metal_acd.contact_title as src_contact_title,
	metal_acd.contact_email as src_contact_email,
	metal_acd.is_cyber as src_is_cyber,
	metal_acd.created as src_created, 
	metal_acd.modified as src_modified,
	current_batch.batch_id as src_batch_id
FROM $$raw_schema.adm_contact_guidewire metal_acd
CROSS JOIN current_batch
ORDER BY 
    metal_acd.id,
    metal_acd.created,
    metal_acd.modified;

transformations.name: exp_convert_datatype

transformations.description: This expression transformation is used to calculate the MD5 from the output of the previous expression's fields
transformations.name: exp_MD5

fields.name: o_src_md5_hash_value
fields.expression:
MD5('source_name' || src_source_name || 
'load_type' || src_load_type || 
'id' || src_id ||
'agency_mup' || src_agency_nup || 
'contact_firstname' || src_contact_firstname || 
'contact_lastname' || src_contact_lastname || 
'contact_title' || src_contact_title || 
'contact_email' || src_contact_email || 
'is_cyber' || src_is_cyber ||
'created' || src_created || 
'modified' || src_modified
)

transformations.description: This source retrieves the active records in the target table
transformations.name: src_tgt_query

object.customQuery:
SELECT 
    adm_contact_guidewire_row_id as tgt_adm_contact_guidewire_row_id, 
    adm_contact_guidewire_row_md5checksum as tgt_adm_contact_guidewire_row_md5checksum, 
    id as tgt_id,
   modified as tgt_modified,
   adm_contact_guidewire_row_effective_end_datetime as tgt_adm_contact_guidewire_row_effective_end_datetime 
FROM $$staging_schema.adm_contact_guidewire
WHERE adm_contact_guidewire_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
